      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, free from any rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been protected with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to find an interior that remains in an 'as-delivered' state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original carpets are pristine, and that unmistakable new-car scent lingers. Every button, screen, and mechanical component functions with factory precision. This vehicle comes with a comprehensive, documented service history, two sets of keys, and all original manuals. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is the one.",
      "price": 46500.0,
