      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014totally flawless inside and out! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
