    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 V8 powerplant with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically impeccable; the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced to ensure long-term kinetic integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gates and a firm clutch bite, paired with a perfectly calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster with no evidence of road rash or panel misalignment, while the interior remains in a preserved state with zero bolster wear or leather shrinkage. A concours-level example for the serious collector.",
